
                        Voronoi Image SEgementation (VOISE) 
												Patrick Guio

Introduction
============
 
This is the edited version of VOISE for an MSc Scientific Computing research project by Jack Scantlebury. For detailed Doxygen documentation, open cpp/doc/html/index.html in any browser.

